Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.94,0:22:55.48,PW,,0,0,0,,{\fs65\fsp200\1c&H8086AB&\pos(761,629)}晚饭
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.42,0:23:03.74,Default,,0,0,0,,配合小青叶
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.72,0:23:06.78,Default,,0,0,0,,变得孩子气一点如何
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.72,0:23:15.17,Default,,0,0,0,,那么变得成熟一点  怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.14,0:23:18.94,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么样
